  "A civil engineer measures forces at 4 points on a truss and records them as vectors in R^3: F1 = (10, 0, 5), F2 = (0, 10, 5), F3 = (10, 10, 10), F4 = (5, 5, 5). She wants to know if any force can be eliminated as redundant (expressible as a combination of the others). Which force is redundant?": "",
