  "A chemist has three chemical solutions represented as concentration vectors: S1 = (2, 1, 0), S2 = (0, 3, 1), S3 = (4, 5, 1) in R^3. She wants to verify she can create any target concentration in the span of these vectors. Are these solutions linearly independent?": "",
